com.mattrader.common

Class OrderManagerCom

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattrader.common.OrderManagerCom

  • public final class OrderManagerCom
extends java.lang.Object
    A manager class for orders. It keep tracks of every order of the client and it provides a method that will propose new unique orderIds on request.
